item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - Nickelodeon's Isa TKM: Greatest Hits + Remixes (16bit/44.1khz)
item.description:
Compilation album of the best of Isa TKM & Isa TK+

Isa TKM is a latin pop group made by Nickelodeon & Sony Pictures Television in order to be the next RBD's, they released two albums, one per season of their telenovela, this novela was broadcasted on the U.S. on MTV Tr3s and on Nickelodeon Latin America, Italy, Israel, Spain & Portugal, also known as Isa TVB in Italy, and Isa ljubim 'Te in Slovenia.
Isa TKM means 'ILY Isa'
